# Welcome aboard

Hi, I'm Jeff ‚ÄĒ also known as OneWheelGeek. Code, wood, unicycles, and self-hosting. This is my capsule: a small, quiet corner of the internet served from one little Go server.

No trackers, no JavaScript, no engagement metrics. Just text, links, and the occasional strong opinion about unnecessary cloud dependencies.

